messages.message:
:fyi-blue: If your dev environment is not able to make calls to OpenAI, it is likely because of a revoked OpenAI API key

• If you are using a crafting `ibdev-backend` sandbox, please follow these instructions (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C05L87V014J/p1741630492761259)!
• If not, you should switch to crafting!

env-local-overrides.json -- env-local-secrets.json is provisioned automatically by Crafting. If you edit it, it will revert back. (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/5ebf1ad058bdd9a9714e0460c1a1f16b0f5ba188/third-party/crafting/templates/ibdev-backend.yml#L118)
oops thanks for the correction! i edited my original message
i edited the original message again since we now have a working key in the `ibdev-backend` template!
